                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
                                        <h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
                                            Doing the Work                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
                                            ‘Anyone who has ever worked night shifts will understand the vertiginous feeling that comes with staring down the day from the wrong end.’<br><br>

A.K. Blakemore on working nights.                                         </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                                        <a href="https://granta.com/doing-the-work-newman/">
                            <div class="recommended-reads__item">
