                                            Doing the Work                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
                                            ‘I was constantly reading job ads, trying to find my holy grail – a job I could stand to do, and someone foolish enough to hire me.’<br><br>

Sandra Newman on learning how to play professional blackjack.                                         </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
