        <div class="row article-contributor-photo-reverse">
          <div class="col-12 col-md-8 flex --direction-col --justify-content-center article-contributor-main">
            <div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
              <h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">David Szalay</h1>
              <p class="article-contributor-section_content">David Szalay was one of <em>Granta</em>’s Best of Young British Novelists in 2013. He is the author of the novels <em>London and the South-East</em>, <em>The Innocent </em>and <em>Spring. </em>He lives in Budapest.</p>
              <a class="article-contributor-section_link" href="https://granta.com/david-szalay">More about the author →</a>
